Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:02.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's get crackin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:03.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's-a-go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:05.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around and start!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.98,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(319,20)}[15th Concert - Symphony No. 9, Opus 125]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.51,0:01:34.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:37.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Got any plans for the end of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this festival and I was wondering if you'd like to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.76,0:01:44.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival for the end of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:46.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it something like a snow festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:54.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to visit relatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I received a similar invitation back during summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:00.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll translate what Konata said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants buddies to buy stuff for her at Comic Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally freaked out by the site when I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:09.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival's a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:14.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all work and no fun by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.99,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(453,218)}Let's Go\Nto the\NFestival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:21.32,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,81)}Dec
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:21.32,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,81)}Heisei 18
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:19.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:21.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Izumi residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:23.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:25.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing New Year's cards right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys in mourning and refusing cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:28.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't get a letter about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:31.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:33.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you absent one day this\Nyear because of a death in the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:39.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:42.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:45.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you used another trick out of manga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiny shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:49.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of cleaning right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hang up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:54.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:04.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:10.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When there's something you don't\Nwant to do, you suddenly want to clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:14.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but once you start cleaning, it suddenly feels like a pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Less resting, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Comiket?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:25.89,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,47)}FIRST-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:26.39,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,47)}FIRST-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:26.89,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(431,47)}FIRST-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was a big festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it sure starts early.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:32.02,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,66)}SECOND-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.27,0:03:32.52,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,66)}SECOND-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:33.02,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,66)}SECOND-TIMER
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you haven't heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.29,0:03:35.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:35.52,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(228,53)}REGULAR-VISITOR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.77,0:03:36.02,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(228,53)}REGULAR-VISITOR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:36.52,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(228,53)}REGULAR-VISITOR
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:36.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get used to it soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:38.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:40.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...this event is gonna exhaust you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in more than one way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:42.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Picking up more and more of her people...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.87,0:04:13.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll soon be allowed to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is kinda scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.49,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,101)\frx6\fry24}Regular Participants
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.49,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(448,103)\frx10\fry18\frz1.026}Circle Members
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:21.49,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(445,267)\frz16.763\frx354\fry26}Industry Members
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should explain your assignments now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Assignments?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,These are your shopping lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:35.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we get inside, we'll split up and go\Naround the circles according to this map.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:37.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You two handle 1-3 in the east building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take 4-6.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't follow the path marked in red...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you might get stuck between rows of displays...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:48.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and end up trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And here and here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're swept into the crowd there...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll be stuck for over half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to work so hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:57.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.42,0:05:02.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones marked with green can wait until afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're stocked up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:06.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so there's almost no danger of them running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:09.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just focus on the ones marked in red before noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:10.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,S stands for something newly published.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:12.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,K stands for something already in print.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.39,0:05:16.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't know what's what, just buy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:20.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to have to pay in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:22.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The coffee will be your only refreshment for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a drink every thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our final rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,1 PM on the dot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait fifteen minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but if you don't show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll go look for you in the medical office so watch the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:34.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:35.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:36.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You only ever sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:40.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...intelligent and passionate when this kind of stuff is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:44.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Climax from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:49.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The limit for new works is four copies per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:50.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is A-92, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:57.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One of each new book?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be 1,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what did you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of these are new...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:05.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.71,0:06:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The new ones would be this and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:08.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Each one is 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:13.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you enjoy the snacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of each please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:19.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dripping Brigade Chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:20.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Naughty Captain, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your total comes to 3,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:26.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.01,0:06:28.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Your total is 4,500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:40.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Locked and loaded...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Onto the next point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:44.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then north should be this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:48.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:49.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wa—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.12,0:06:53.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:57.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've pretty much covered all the big places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The next place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a peek...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gauron and Sousuke are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:23.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:26.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too intense for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:35.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary Girl A!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:37.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll think we're weird if we panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a weird jinx...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.75,0:07:46.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...where every circle suddenly becomes big after she buys a book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to stay calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:49.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:52.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we put so much effort into this book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So she would buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:55.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it was the end of the year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we skipped work to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This year will be our year!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:15.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:20.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We put a lot of work into the concert scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:23.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Iffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:25.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thankssomuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Next summer for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.49,0:08:34.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:35.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:40.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Pu-61 located?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:40.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Pu in the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:44.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the east building?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the west building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the east building...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...get in that line there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go up one floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:53.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:54.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, probably an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:01.72,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,235)\frz339.191}Please wait one moment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, I'm done.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:11.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just now got back from the west building.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:15.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You get completely lost after getting caught up in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in this event...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.51,0:09:19.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to wait in line for an hour to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:19.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:23.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would be a rought schedule for a first-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so let's just stroll around for the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not done yet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:29.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.71,0:09:34.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's gotten a lot better since they moved this to Ariake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.24,0:09:38.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They only had two convenience stores near the site at Harumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Site at Harumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The last one at Harumi was twelve years ago, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:45.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How old were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Around five?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad took me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:54.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We always stayed at this place called Hotel Urashima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My first time was at the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:59.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was one crazy second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweat from all the participants evaporated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and turned into these fluffy steam clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:06.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:07.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's gotten a lot easier after they moved this to Ariake...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:14.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but maybe it's 'cause of the people mainly here for events...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:19.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...many of the younger participants think\Nof themselves as customers, sadly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:23.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This was supposed to be an event put on by all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt you while you're on a roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:26.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you've totally lost me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.15,0:10:33.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't come here during summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:35.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they also have places like these, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:34.61,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The main stuff is probably all sold out though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Nagato! Nagato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The person behind Nagamon is here as a salesgirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.04,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be out of Haruhi goods?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I bother coming here if the\NNagato phone cards are sold out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:53.04,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.21,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:57.13,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm never coming back to this dump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:53.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a spike in people like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, our limited goods...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...have already sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you're gonna show up this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:09.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you gotta line up early...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.92,0:11:13.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.67,0:11:15.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Asia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.30,0:11:18.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even customers who show up late...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:22.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...must be completely satisfied!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:24.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost the true spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,All we have is leftover stuff now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Leftover items still have value!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A value that can't be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...in popular items and mainstream turn-ons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This Comiket exists to reveal their true value!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:48.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that all limited goods have been eliminated...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the true battle has begun for industry booths!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,B-By George...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a recommendation to the customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig up your true item!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I can use as a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:05.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:09.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta be this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:10.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagato and everybody else is selling like hotcakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:15.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Koizumi's sells well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:17.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's gone unsold for three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the Captain's sold out instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So please purchase this Kyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I recommend Sousuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wanted CoCo Saikoubi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:27.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,President Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:36.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takahashi the President!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:40.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I overheard your conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:45.24,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your desire to promote a new perspecive of value is commendable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.37,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.70,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I cannot forgive your selfish desire to promote unpopular characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That place is always pumped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.72,0:12:51.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:52.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both main characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:08.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, I'm sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:10.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sleepy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:14.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We had to help out at home as soon as we got back from Ariake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do they have that event on New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:18.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:21.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:27.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an awful lot of energy for\Nsomeone who was at that event since morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, it's cold, so I figured you wouldn't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:33.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but January 1st is a new beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:37.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I have to come charge up for the coming year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's what Dad said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:41.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:43.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Suddenly, I'm disturbed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrine maiden outfits are so invigorating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:50.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys do any praying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:56.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You were doing some intense praying, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:01.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go blabbing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't that intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:08.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was just hoping I could be in the\Nsame class as you and Miyuki this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.47,0:14:12.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:13.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami's actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You making fun of everything is why I never want to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's the way you resist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:25.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis has always been the only one in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Ms. Kuroi hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:30.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also pray...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...to be in the same class...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:33.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...as Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami needs to be in a different class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.64,0:14:39.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:41.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That way I can borrow stuff from you when I forget mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't get caught if I copy your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:48.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you're in our class, my rank will go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you go be in a different class by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:52.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:53.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sebastian was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.70,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Female students are so wonderful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:15:00.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to draw your fortune this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.63,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(249,81)}[Bad]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:03.63,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(378,79)}[Very Good]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:06.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to get an early start on the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:07.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I got to see something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a good year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:13.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've already hit rock bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.56,0:15:17.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...things can only get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Something good will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It all depends on how you word it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:23.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to tie a bad luck ward on the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:31.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:40.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the power of bad luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:41.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not something good will happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...depends on the amount of effort you spend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing your fortune is just a game of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.65,0:15:52.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Although a staff member shouldn't be saying that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:58.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should go for a whole set from very good to very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they supposed to be trading cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you can draw a secret fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What would a secret fortune be like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like ultra bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:09.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you go with something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:14.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever collects all of them gets a special item!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:16.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.49,0:16:17.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:27.42,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[kagami mochi: two stacked rice cakes; traditional New Year's decoration]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:20.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw a huge kagami mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that where your name came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not totally wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The round shape of a kagami mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...is modeled after a mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:35.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's long been said that gods rest within mirrors...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:39.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so the name is supposed to invoke the blessings of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And the round shape also signifies family happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her name has such a fantastic origin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...yet she grew up to be an awfully pragmatic person!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:56.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's New Year's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Though we aren't that well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:13.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many of them are\Nhere for the shrine maidens like Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here we go again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There aren't that many!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:34.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have another wonderful year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:41.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:42.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:45.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:47.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this beautiful sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.15,0:17:55.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all the pretty flowers everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.87,0:18:00.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:08.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:09.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:16.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:20.78,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}[zoni soup: a broth eaten with rice cakes; New Year's meal]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:19.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some zoni soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:20.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.28,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(366,85)\frz345.604}NEW YEAR'S
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:22.28,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(329,229)\frz344.763}ALLOWANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:28.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he likes how I keep scurrying over until I get my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are really close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:36.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And I managed to get my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I'm planning on going to Gamers right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that all of those shops are in the city is a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already on a tight budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the train fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:50.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish they'd open a shop near us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:54.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't a lot of stores sell online now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you could try that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:02.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get points when you order online...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:07.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but browsing through the store and\Nmaking unexpected discoveries is what's really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally ready to spend it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:12.58,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The radishes are almost completely done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:14.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now we'll put this completely in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:15.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why this is called a pochi bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's from the phrases pochitto (a\Nsmidge) and korepocchi (just a bit).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:21.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It refers to a bag you put small stuff in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pochitto would be Kansai...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and korepocchi would be Kanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.56,0:19:35.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.42,0:19:38.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:39.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was wondering where the name pochi bag came from...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.07,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Konata...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.12,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Can't you have a little more faith in your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.12,0:19:50.25,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And couldn't you do that somewhere out of sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:44.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pochi bag, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:48.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it came from the phrases pochitto and korepocchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and refers to a bag for small items.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.69,0:19:57.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to wish everyone in the game a happy new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:09.39,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mess and all. In the end\NI wasn't able to buy any Haruhi goods...\NDon't cry!\NYour friend konakona has logged on\NOh?\NHappy New Year!\NYeah, Happy New Year! >w<b\NCongratslololo\NFinally got on. Been busy for a while
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:21.61,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year, Teacher\NYo, Happy New Year! (^w^)ノ\NLet's have another wonderful year
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:21.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:24.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always online...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.55,0:20:26.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't she have anything else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:28.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that's why she doesn't have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:36.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Go—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:38.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Minoru Shirashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already on the twelfth episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This sea is hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:48.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:50.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:54.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...Akira-sama was supposed to\Nappear in the actual show this week...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:56.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she suddenly became ill...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:07.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I put up a cardboard pop-up instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so if you go look carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:15.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:17.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:20.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it looks like Akira-sama's already tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we'll have to call it a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:23.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.24,0:21:24.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bee!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely not getting full of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:31.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let you hear the new version of {\i1}Take it! Sailor Uniform{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So look forward to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.50,0:21:36.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't watch next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll turn into Mars and scold you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:39.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We got pretty into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:46.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.93,0:21:49.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's ordered a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it your turn?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:52.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is when you're supposed to order a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.93,0:21:54.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't choose one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also a menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.94,0:22:04.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you can also eat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:04.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:08.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That song totally broke my flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should have saved it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:11.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What flow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.45,0:22:12.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:16.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How you sometimes feel like you sing better?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.25,0:22:17.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.42,0:22:18.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if I can sing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:22.73,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.32,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Godman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.32,0:22:27.45,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:29.07,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:30.82,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Godman!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.82,0:22:33.08,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:28.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tambourine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:32.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:33.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:34.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:35.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:36.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.10,0:22:37.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even a hardcore anime song will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:38.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:41.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I ordered an exciting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:46.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.40,0:22:47.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:48.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:50.43,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Do—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.43,0:22:51.26,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:09.99,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,It was spur of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:13.37,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(149,5)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.47,0:23:13.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:14.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.81,0:23:16.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When something has completely outstripped the competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:19.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and stands heads above the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:22.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...we use the word {\i1}dantotsu{\i0} to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.36,0:23:25.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's apparently short for {\i1}danzen{\i0} (on the very) top.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:28.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This word first appeared in literature...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...after the recent city election...
